OL,4,Cher mini-budget in King's Speech
OL,5,Cdocument
OL,7,FLiz Truss has hit out at civil
OL,8,Fservants after her "disastrous" mini-
OL,9,Fbudget was labelled a "disaster" in
OL,10,Fgovernment documents about the King's
OL,11,FSpeech on Wednesday.
OL,13,FThe former prime minister complained
OL,14,Fthat references to the "mistakes" of
OL,15,Fher economic policy, which unleashed
OL,16,Fchaos in the markets, tanked the pound
OL,17,Fand caused mortgage rates to
OL,18,Fskyrocket, were "untrue political
OL,19,Fattacks".
