OL,7,FAlongside the speech, a briefing
OL,8,Fdocument outlining more details about
OL,9,Fthe new laws was published on the
OL,10,Fgovernment website.
OL,12,FMs Truss wrote to the head of the
OL,13,Fcivil service complaining that the
OL,14,Flanguage around her actions was "more
OL,15,Fevidence of a lack of civil service
OL,16,Fimpartiality."
