OL,7,FIn a letter to Simon Case, the head of
OL,8,Fthe civil service, Ms Truss urged him
OL,9,Fto "urgently investigate how such
OL,10,Fmaterial came to be included in this
OL,11,Fdocument, ensure suitable admonishment
OL,12,Ffor those responsible and the
OL,13,Fimmediate removal of such political
OL,14,Fmaterial from the version of the
OL,15,Fdocument on gov.uk".
