OL,7,FMs Truss, who is no longer an MP after
OL,8,Fsuffering a crushing defeat in her
OL,9,FNorfolk constituency in the general
OL,10,Felection, said: "It has been brought
OL,11,Fto my attention that the King's Speech
OL,12,Fbackground briefing notes published
OL,13,Ftoday and available online contain
OL,14,Frepeated references personally to me
OL,15,Fand actions undertaken by my
OL,16,Fgovernment in the context of a
OL,17,Fpolitical attack.
