OL,7,F"Not only is what is stated in the
OL,8,Fdocument untrue, making no reference
OL,9,Fto the LDI crisis precipitated by the
OL,10,FBank of England's regulatory failures;
OL,11,Fbut I regard it as a flagrant breach
OL,12,Fof the civil service code, since such
OL,13,Fpersonal and political attacks have no
OL,14,Fplace in a document prepared by civil
OL,15,Fservants ` an error made all the more
OL,16,Fegregious when the attack is allowed
OL,17,Fto masquerade in the document among
OL,18,F'key facts'."
