OL,7,FThe briefing document had referred to
OL,8,Fthe "disaster" of Ms Truss's radical
OL,9,Ftax-cutting agenda and cites the
OL,10,FInstitute for Government think tank as
OL,11,Fsaying the mini-budget was "a lesson
OL,12,Fin how not to do fiscal policy".
OL,14,FA section of the document outlining
OL,15,Fthe Budget Responsibility Bill ` which
OL,16,Fwould seek to strengthen the role of
OL,17,Fthe Office for Budget Responsibility
OL,18,F(OBR) ` proposes that significant and
OL,19,Fpermanent changes to tax and spend
OL,20,Fwould be subject to an independent
OL,21,Fassessment by the Treasury watchdog.
