OL,7,FThis would be introduced "to ensure
OL,8,Fthat the mistakes of Liz Truss 'mini
OL,9,Fbudget' cannot be repeated", the
OL,10,Fbriefing says.
OL,12,FSince being ejected from Number 10
OL,13,Fafter just 49 days in office ` making
OL,14,Fher Britain's shortest-serving prime
OL,15,Fminister ` Ms Truss has conceded her
OL,16,Fplan to quickly abolish the 45p top
OL,17,Frate of tax went too far, but
OL,18,Fotherwise defended her failed bid to
OL,19,Fboost growth.
